{"tid":854121,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]Dragalia Lost ～失落的龍絆～ 今晚有裸體lily（27）","createTime":"2018-10-09T06:51:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T06:52:46.000Z","uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cc2b0807d05cc970425d2b4c635e52a1b223f6da","tid":854121,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140701_72ff37b86353e5a812ff1ede8b67764e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140701_72ff37b86353e5a812ff1ede8b67764e.png&h=ef001d0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">任天堂與 Cygames 合作研發的智慧型手機遊戲《Dragalia Lost ～失落的龍絆～》，使用與您締結契約的龍族之力而戰的「龍化」。華麗多樣的動作、技能與龍化時機都由您一手操作，擊敗種種強敵。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>最新活動：</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/142308_18aa73b4321ca80dd5d02302215d6f4d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F142308_18aa73b4321ca80dd5d02302215d6f4d.png&h=232478d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">10 月 4 日（四）14 : 00 起舉辦團體活動「忠龍祈願故王的靈魂葬禮」，本活動可在團隊遊戲模式下挑戰火屬性的團體戰 BOSS。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>活動注意事項：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><ins>打法</ins></strong><br />\n<em>首先要斷尾，再去打其他部位，Overdrive時火山要打最少兩座！呢句一定要記住！<br />\n<br />\n王出黃圈技既時候，係發動前出技可以迴避；紫色圈無得出技避，打爆火山係最好解決方法，唔斷尾會有多招紫圈！<br />\n<br />\n打EX果陣最好overdrive時留晒三招技，以防連續龍車</em></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>入場需求：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">EX : 主戰力2000分或以上<br />\nHard : 總戰力7000分或以上</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>補充：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">活動角色十分有用，一定要升，抽唔到利維坦既朋友點都要用條水龍去加攻，活動張都護符唔裝就拖出去打靶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外帶火入場既你都預左比人NG，唔好問點解！<br />\n<br />\n點開EX???? <br />\n做場主開場打Hard平均兩場會出現一次! 答左太多次，唔好再問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">(你個野壞左呀)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n抽戰貨係咪拎到條龍就reset得????<br />\n係，除非你對內容有須求，你淨係想要條龍既抽到就可以reset</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;&minus;</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140711_b249210ec5ddc893f15f5f3ef662da69.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140711_b249210ec5ddc893f15f5f3ef662da69.png&h=1bc5b2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140720_4f87d25f9d6256f4a84497db6bdba564.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140720_4f87d25f9d6256f4a84497db6bdba564.png&h=51271aec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140733_f989b1cb06829f08f08f34d075e26037.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140733_f989b1cb06829f08f08f34d075e26037.png&h=f54c71dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140742_275df6919db76ae6dbc8fd40a04b5db6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140742_275df6919db76ae6dbc8fd40a04b5db6.png&h=8c4902ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140809_bbfda0799f1d03d2d9daa8444a46dea0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140809_bbfda0799f1d03d2d9daa8444a46dea0.png&h=2de2d11b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140820_11e7eb6d5c92850eb36fb3068c94272f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140820_11e7eb6d5c92850eb36fb3068c94272f.png&h=fed5f542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140830_b53edcf3d3cf3d56e68d742dab4d3fde.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140830_b53edcf3d3cf3d56e68d742dab4d3fde.png&h=4f88a65b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/140840_9555427561d87ceab84424e5d29a05cf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F140840_9555427561d87ceab84424e5d29a05cf.png&h=39be2ead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/watch?v=RKA40l2zGTg&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRKA40l2zGTg%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=lb9mAeaxn1WEdioOs5bZisPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=1fdc52ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/watch?v=RKA40l2zGTg&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>首抽：</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">可以參考以下連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/j5do23\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fj5do23&d=lb9mAeaxn1WEdioOs5bZisPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=cddf3820\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/j5do23</a> (轉載自巴哈龍絆板)<br />\n五星既一龍一角就基本<br />\n龍黎講不死鳥幾乎係必須，人物就岩手勢既五星就得<br />\n<br />\n評價網:<br />\n<a href=\"https://game8.jp/dragalialost/233911\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame8.jp%2Fdragalialost%2F233911&d=lb9mAeaxn1WEdioOs5bZisPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=1ab2c49f\" target=\"_blank\">https://game8.jp/dragalialost/233911</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>FAQ：</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">同人合作打有幾多石？<br />\n50石一個人，最多2500石<br />\n<br />\n點升戰力？<br />\n升lvl／升環／龍／武器／建築／護符<br />\n<br />\n點有多啲瑪那？<br />\n課金以外任何關卡都會提供<br />\n<br />\n點造高星武？<br />\n升建築lvl再升主城同鍛造<br />\n<br />\n唔夠錢點算？<br />\n打錢副本</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>其他須知事項：</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">爆發攻擊(蓄力)可以破盾，也可以大幅減少OD(技能槽)<br />\n<br />\n紅色預警圈可以使用技能無敵幀擋住，紫色的不行<br />\n昏迷&mdash;&mdash;受到攻擊後方可解除<br />\n黑暗&mdash;&mdash;命中率下降<br />\n濕身&mdash;&mdash;必被暴擊<br />\n冰凍&mdash;&mdash;被同伴攻擊後可解除</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aYYRo2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaYYRo2b.png&h=840bfb17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首抽推薦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n莉莉、光奶、光斧<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/105551_ba600461034f4a911e4caa6f5146fc76.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F105551_ba600461034f4a911e4caa6f5146fc76.png&h=10063ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n火刀女<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/105459_127dbc08891f2c5d801fa59ec6f87681.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F105459_127dbc08891f2c5d801fa59ec6f87681.gif&h=bd896583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n水槍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nY01aws.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnY01aws.jpg&h=e912a611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n風弓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ranu3RT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Franu3RT.jpg&h=cdc02cbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暗弓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h3SGayd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh3SGayd.jpg&h=d29b9437&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09657bfdea95e6abdb6dd8c6173f127e4e16b358","tid":854121,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:52:23.000Z","msg":"又27?"},{"pid":"505301ce9c2cb77b2587b905ea16f398855b08f5","tid":854121,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09657bfdea95e6abdb6dd8c6173f127e4e16b358","tid":854121,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:52:23.000Z","msg":"又27?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:52:38.000Z","msg":"sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7ca43741fd0e68aefe924b52e10b59c5ab3889","tid":854121,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:52:46.000Z","msg":"再開過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}